Transatlantic Says Buffett May Make Better Proposal

-- B y   V i v e k   S h a n k a r
-- 
2011-08-08T23:39:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-08/transatlantic-says-buffett-offer-may-lead-to-a-better-proposal.html
(Corrects to says Allied World’s offer is superior, not
 Validus Holdings Ltd. (VR) ’s.)  Transatlantic Holdings Inc. (TRH)  said an
offer from a unit of Warren Buffett’s  Berkshire Hathaway Inc. (BRK/A) 
isn’t better than one from Allied World Assurance Company
Holdings AG. Still, the bid is “likely to lead to a superior
proposal,” Transatlantic said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
